        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-07-16T13:57:30Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Neighborhood Investment Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from gross income gain from the sale of single-family residential rental property held by a taxpayer for two years or more and rented as a single dwelling unit on a regular basis during the five-year period prior to its sale. Limits the amount of such exclusion to $250,000.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
